{"id":74964,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2010/05/自由亚洲：香港法院拒受理“毒奶粉”索赔-家长指/","date":"2010-05-27T18:07:41Z","modified":"2010-09-13T21:04:46Z","title":"自由亚洲：香港法院拒受理“毒奶粉”索赔 家长指肾损伤不可逆转(视频)","content":"<p>中国四名三鹿毒奶粉受害患儿的家长入禀香港小额钱债审裁处，向三鹿集团第二大股东、新西兰恒天然集团在香港的分公司索偿，星期四审裁处裁定撤销诉讼。家长的代表律师表示失望，会考虑上诉。结石患儿家长指，肾结石造成的损伤，已不可逆转。自由亚洲电台特约记者乔龙的采访报道</p>\n<p><object classid=\"clsid:d27cdb6e-ae6d-11cf-96b8-444553540000\" width=\"480\" height=\"385\" codebase=\"http://download.macromedia.com/pub/shockwave/cabs/flash/swflash.cab#version=6,0,40,0\"><param name=\"allowFullScreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"src\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/4j08Hj8kKeU&amp;hl=en_US&amp;fs=1&amp;\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><embed type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"480\" height=\"385\" src=\"http://www.youtube.com/v/4j08Hj8kKeU&amp;hl=en_US&amp;fs=1&amp;\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></embed></object></p>\n<p>&#8230;&#8230;</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/dunai-05272010101350.html\">http://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/dunai-05272010101350.html</a></p>\n","author":251,"categories":[20534],"tags":[3764,10780,9561,9314,9204,8712]}